data.description: Welcome to this stunning property nestled in the desirable Madera Highlands community. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with 1820 sq ft, this home offers an extra versatile area that can easily adapt to your needs - whether it's a dedicated teen space, a flexible room for work or play, or a cozy dining area for entertaining.As you step into the spacious interior, you'll be greeted by the timeless elegance of luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main areas, offering both durability and style. Natural light pours in, illuminating the inviting atmosphere and creating a warm ambiance.Situated on a corner lot, this residence offers unparalleled privacy and convenience and don't forget the breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains from your new backyard. Come see today!
